    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 58-61.</p><p>Primeval Burst</p><p>Also at 24th level, your critical range is increased by 1. When you score a critical hit, you can expend a 5th-level spell slot to imbue the attack with the power of the wild and deal an additional 100 points of Lethal damage. This extra damage is not doubled (or tripled) by the critical hit. If you have no 5th-level spell slots remaining, you can expend 1 Legendary Point instead.</p></div>",
